name: Heavy Estarayo
customPrimary: Explodes on contact or after reaching maximum range, dealing 300 High Explosive damage in an area. Explosion size and damage dealt reduced under under 800 range, with explosion not taking place if distance to target is 250 or smaller.

name: Medium Estarayo
customPrimary: Explodes on contact or after reaching maximum range, dealing 120 High Explosive damage in an area. Explosion size and damage dealt reduced under under 700 range, with explosion not taking place if distance to target is 150 or smaller.

name: Light Estarayo
customPrimary: Explodes on contact or after reaching maximum range, dealing 60 High Explosive damage in an area. Explosion size and damage dealt reduced under under 600 range, with explosion not taking place if distance to target is 50 or smaller.
